metadata.name: Portals part 1
metadata.description:
There is an endless cycle of color and form. There is a portal captivating with its mystery. 
An unknown, and therefore even more attractive reality, is waiting for someone to pass through it.
The Portal is a symbiosis of all decisions made and the outcome of events. Passing through it, we get rid of stereotypes and see a way out of the limiting mindsets.
Every turn and every action starts a new round in the creation of a new reality. This is a unique experience that gives birth to a beautiful flower of life
